"Calibrate" tool for the WizardPen tablet driver for XOrg/XFree86
=================================================================

Installation
------------

See the INSTALL file for detailed installation instructions.


Compatibility
-------------

This tool should work with all Genius WizardPen and MousePen series
tablets. Other Genius USB tablets may be working too, please report any
experience with it, if you have one.

Usage
-----

Execute and follow on-screen instructions:

wizardpen-calibrate <wizardpen event device>

Where, "wizardpen event device" is one of /dev/input/eventX which
corresponds to your tablet, or a symlink created by udev rule (if you have
written one).

